# NSPrintPanel.JobStyleHint

**Structure**

Constants that specify job style hints for activating the simplified Print panel interface and setting the options to display.

## Declaration

```swift
struct JobStyleHint
```

## Constants

- **photo**: Output contains photographic data.
- **allPresets**: Output appropriate to all graphics types.
- **noPresets**: Output excludes all graphics printing.

## Initializers

- **init(rawValue:)**: Creates a new instance with the specified raw value.

## Customizing the Panel

- **jobStyleHint**: The type of settings that the print panel displays.
- **options**: The current configuration options for the Print panel.
- **NSPrintPanel.Options**: Constants that specify options for configuring the contents of the main Print panel.
- **defaultButtonTitle()**: Returns the title of the Print panel’s default button.
- **setDefaultButtonTitle(_:)**: Sets the title of the Print panel’s default button.
- **helpAnchor**: The HTML help anchor associated with the Print panel.

- Equatable
- Hashable
- RawRepresentable
- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
